title: KILLING EVE - S1 Ep 1 & 2
body:
I’m home sick with a medium-bad cold which seems like a good excuse to hunker down with this one!! I’m gonna post reacts in pairs okie? And you might probably get another set before the day is out because like I am leaving my fainting couch.

KILLING EVE

“Two women, a psychopathic assassin and a brilliant MI5 agent. Both tasked with the same deadly mission: Find Her.” omg this already RULES

Season 1, Episode 1 - ‘Nice Face’

boom chyron: “VIENNA.” I love it

what a fantastic opening scene

what a fantastic Sandra Oh!

her oooutfiiiit

wait is that Simone from The Good Place??

it IS Simone from The Good Place!!

did Eve’s boss just give her the “eh? what do you think?” eyebrows at this swimsuit model?

I love that she’s the unpolished mid-40s absent-minded professor sort of brilliant, MAN do we rarely get female versions of that!

I love everyone in this bar?

her apartment, that she put on ERIK SATIE’S WEIRD GNOSSIENNES

is that a tiny bullet proof vest or a binder?

haha alright, this assassin-handler relaysh. both women have good relationships with their male supervisors.

yeesss, bringing in the youth, this is such a Sherlock Holmes consulting the street urchins moment

“I was counting on you not having a life.” Eve omg.

ID THROUGH BOOBS. ID THROUGH BOOBS. ID THROUGH BOOBS.

anyway, binder then!

god Villanelle’s always eating, it’s the best. she just, SQUEEZED that tomato over her bruschetta. where did she even get that she’s in the middle of the Tuscan countryside! what an icon.

lol he’s got one of the Guido Reni St. Sebastians

yeah Eve, try out the stabs on yourself why don’t ya! god she’s such a nut A+

husband is Great, I like him

“You should have been a spy.”
“Exactly, thank you!”

oh hello, look at this bea-utiful threesome

also, tight tight: they’ve cut from Eve in bed to Villanelle in bed. twinning!!

she’s so PLAYFUL, <3 ludic asocial lady assassin

“Our job is weird, but it’s also boring.” wow sounds like television. sounds like ALL JOBS.

yeeeyeyeysss, oh jesus i love the homoerotic killer/detective vibe always. Villanelle looking at Sandra Oh’s hair like “oh shit.”

oh thank GOD that wee fever-flushed Polish boy is okay!!!

hahaha, Eve and Frank are so cute. cute and fired.

Russian spy leader is totes gonna offer them a job though. sidle up all “it seems like they don’t appreciate you. I Would.”

Eve catch up! if you wanna be a secret agent you gotta learn tradecraft!

this show is so genuinely very funny though, bless a joke, all shows should have jokes

Sandra Oh says “melk”!!!! like meeeee until I trained myself out of it! hi dialect buddy!! apparently eastern Canada shares this with the Pacific Northwest?

“Right. Buy some milk. Otherwise he’ll think you’re having an affair.”
“Ohh, I don’t think, he’d ever think that.”
“They all think we’re having affairs before they think we’re secret agents.”
“Oh no I think Niko would assume I was an agent before ever thinking I was having an affair ha ha.”
“You might want to make him think you’re having an affair then.”
CAN I GO OFF! ON ALL THE WAYS I ADORE THIS!
1. hilarity, see earlier re: bless a joke
2. such a fun way to tell someone they’re about to become a real special agent!!!
3. Eve/Niko character development
4. Eve/Villanelle sly metatextual flirty positioning~~

Appreciating Food & Coveting Fine Things: Correlation or Causation With Murder? The Hannibal & Killing Eve Thesis

Season 1, Episode 2 - ‘I’ll Deal With Him Later’

hahaha, oh you know this girl on the bus is just thinking “eh I’m sure he deserves it”

“Who are you?”
“Huge question.”
wonderful

sure, Connecticut. (not with that accent!)

LOL, Eve all “oh you just found my obsessive assassin dossiers! man I was worried it was all the office memes”

wait hold on, just occurring to me that ~Carolyn Martens~ had this whole restaurant emptied for them. BALLER. and this server just called her “madam” in a way that sounded more like an honorific than anything else.

!!! Eve!! she literally just said she feels like this assassin has outsmarted their smartest so she should be allowed to kill whoever she wants! YOU ARE A MARVELOUS DARWINIAN WEIRDO

Carolyn: “I once saw a rat drink from a can of Coke there. Both hands. Extraordinary.” this show is now my baby

oh that’s the face of a woman looking a Wall

ding ding ding!!

Eve sincerely thanking people who tell her things like “You should have been a spy” or “You make insane suggestions” is my favorite thing

“I recommend small ones.” THIS SHOW IS SO FUNNY

VILLANELLE’S CLOTHES THOUGH. these big pink pants….

“drinking from a tiny cup”

I like how she’s so beautiful but so odd looking at the same time

these men do NOT know what to make of her! (“Who are you?” / “Huge question.”!)

ooo who’s Anna, what’s the story!

she likes…national anthems

yaaaaassss I was hoping Eve would bring along Bill and Elena

“Quitting is literally everything I’ve been aiming for!” Elena. <3

Greco, wait— maybe that was supposed to be an El Greco St. Sebastian that hairpin dude had??? and he’s like, an offspring??!

I mean Bill does actually make a good point, with this bit about undermining your investigation as soon as you *want* to believe something

she is seriously always eating

wow she’s brilliant. classic tampon maneuv, makes all the men stop asking questions RIGHT away

charming. what an incredible murder.

what an incredible wheezing, gasping murder

Elena. <3 <3

lol Eve tells her husband after the very first day

asldfjalfjk

he gave her….a USB with national anthems. you poor sweet dead idiot.

twinning again! they’re both searching for the other’s face on their computers!!! NOICE

uh oh Vill it’s your crush!!!

tossing your laptop to your side and looking at it askew because wtf is So Relatable, wow, been there

T B C
